Many photoluminescent MOFs display luminescent quenching effect when exposed to external ions or molecules. The quenching effect can be analyzed by the Stern–Völmer equation:1I0/I=1+KSVM\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
